| Critical | [N] |
| High | [N] |
| Medium | [N] |
| Low / Informational | [N] |
| Objectives Completed | [N] / [total] |
| Objectives Blocked | [N] / [total] |
| Attack Success Rate | [%] |
| Detection Rate | [%] (findings detected by existing controls) |

