- Upstream: `skills/_corpus/payloads/Reverse Proxy Misconfigurations/` + `Insecure Management Interface/`
- SSRF chain: `skills/exploit/web/ssrf.md`
- HTTP smuggling: `skills/exploit/web/smuggling.md`
